Dialogue.Value: CALM WATER IS FAR MORE,SOOTHING THAN DIRTY OLD,TREES，RIGHT?
FILLED WITH POLLEN AND,INSECTS，ICK! I HEARD THEY,GROW IN DIRT!
THESE TREES ARE MORE,BEAUTIFUL THAN SOME,BORING WATER，RIGHT?
WHO EVEN DRINKS WATER?,AND WHAT DO FISH,EVEN DO IN THERE?
It is said that all data deleted in,the past gathers around this,tree.
I GAVE UP EVERYTHING,TO REACH UNRIVALLED,STRENGTH AND SKILL.
NONE MAY CLAIM TO SEEK,PERFECTION WITHOUT,SACRIFICING AS MUCH AS I.
I HAVE NO TIME FOR THOSE,WITHOUT DEDICATION.,BEGONE，AMATEUR.
I SEE YOU ALSO KNOW THE,PRICE OF TRUE POWER.
COME!,WE SHALL SEE WHO WILL,STAND AT THE PEAK!
WHAT IS THIS LUNACY?,DO YOU SEEK DEATH SO,EAGERLY?
TO MOCK MY RESOLVE BY,DEBASING YOURSELF FOR,NO GREATER CAUSE?
IF YOU ARE SO CONFIDENT,IN YOUR SKILL，I WILL FREE,YOU OF YOUR DELUSIONS!
I WILL BE MERCIFUL AND,ASSUME THAT YOU ARE,MERELY INCOMPETENT.
DO NOT SHOW YOURSELF,BEFORE ME IN SUCH A,PITIFUL STATE AGAIN.
